<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Encurtador</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" alt="Encurtador" class="icon"/>
        <h1>Aqui está o resultado do encurtamento:</h1>
        
      </div>

      <div class="telaResposta">      
        <p>
            <b>
                http://localhost:3000/<%= code %>
            </b>
        </p>

        <p>
            <br/>Redireciona para:<br/><br/>
            <%= url%>
        </p>
        <br/>

        <p>Copie e cole o endereço encurtado nesta ou em outra aba para ser redirecionado para a url original.</p><br/>

        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary" >Encurtar nova url</a>
        
      </div>

    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </body>
</html>
